title: 2021 Week 11 Preview
itunes:title: 2021 Week 11 Preview
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview every single upcoming game of Week 11, starting with the primetime games. Dan kicks off the draft with an NFC North showdown, Marc makes a shocking move with the second pick, and Gregg somehow nabs the game of the week, plus Week 11 locks!
